{"tid":668150,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個港奴同事","createTime":"2018-05-17T11:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T15:44:46.000Z","uid":4353,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b9de7fcdc5e3b129a9d342e283a02267909fba7f","tid":668150,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"話說我公司返工時間係朝早8:15嘅，有次返星期六，有個A同事就帶埋早餐返公司食啦<br />\n<br />\n之後個A同事話佢比人報串食早餐食到8:20多啲時間，話過咗開工時間都仲食緊早餐<br />\n<br />\n而報串嗰個同事仲係直接同大老世講嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但大老世冇咩理，只係低調叫人同番呀A講盡量喺8:15前食晒去，過咗時間就要做番公司野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜而家啲港奴同事咁撚癡線，好似小學雞舉手同老師講有人上堂偷食野咁，心諗人地放工唔走OT又唔見你向老世報？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵做一世港奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f283432b6df6194e93eb9dd0f1ec92fb210949df","tid":668150,"uid":51291,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"要刷存在感搵你地開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba7311c4cb48844abd804929b2bb9466f39c57e","tid":668150,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"成件事好癡線<br />\n報串有分加咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要報埋啲on9野"},{"pid":"eaf2d333f030a6ccefc21bfd7b438c9d99411c1b","tid":668150,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文革咩屌佢"},{"pid":"7fa0327c546a0d79cedabba490e9f79af84bfa9c","tid":668150,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"唔止港奴，仲要覺得主動報串好醒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓身為公司咁"},{"pid":"8ebed6e52cd2906ce161d1a3633e1bac974ca627","tid":668150,"uid":4353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e66020fecc7e6675ea4f95b55559a299f45b3ec6","tid":668150,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bbe71f62a6028e1e7295db4f0a184c34fdb275","tid":668150,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲狗先上位得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}